outputs.output_descr: The project is to provide technical assistance and capacity development support to achieve the government's accelerated poverty reduction targets in the poorest ethnic minority, mountainous and coastal areas.

project_descr: “Support to the implementation of the Resolution 80/NQ-CP on directions of sustainable poverty reduction 2011-2020 and the National Targeted Program on Sustainable Poverty Reduction 2012-2015”
project_title: Support to the implementation of the Resolution 80
